        "Fe-Mn-Al-C alloy",
        "Compositional design",
        "κ-carbide",
        "Machine-learning"
      ],
      "research_type": "mixed",
      "paper_scope": "Establish the correlation between composition and microstructure of low-density FeMnAlC steel using machine learning algorithms, predict four key characteristics (existence of κ phase, (γ+κ) dual-phase region at 500-600 °C aging temperature, single γ phase region, volume fraction of κ phase), and validate the prediction accuracy with Fe-30Mn-8Al-1C steel experiments."
    }
