  "unmapped_findings": [
    "When Mn content is fixed at 30 wt%, minimum Al content of ~4 wt% is required to guarantee existence of κ phase.",
    "Al and C content range for (γ + κ) duplex region at 500-600 °C aging is 4.5-9.3 wt% Al and 0.4-1.1 wt% C.",
    "78477 initial composition candidates were screened, 1320 candidates met phase requirements (Y1, Y2, Y3), 150 candidates met κ phase volume fraction ≥10% and density ≤7 g/cm³ requirements.",
    "Fe-30Mn-8Al-1C steel experimental results are in good agreement with machine learning prediction results, verifying the reliability of the proposed design method.",
    "The proposed machine learning assisted composition design method is applicable to other metallic material systems."
  ]
